title: The Growth & Development of the McMichael Art Collection
creator: Qashoa, Nada; Spagnuolo, Alessia
description: In this podcast, we will be exploring the history of the McMichael Canadian Art Collection in Kleinburg, Ontario. The main topics discussed in this podcast include how the museum defines what is Canadian art, how this definition has changed over the years, and how this notion of nationality has affected the types of exhibits produced.
